content:
When I saw you running over with your fishing rod,
I believe I heard the sound of fish swiftly swimming away.
Next time, you'll need to tread more lightly.{开心}

Yip-yip-yip~! With that fishing rod in your hands,
Will you engage in a solemn battle with wind and waves?
Or perhaps frolic with the fish and shrimp in the shallows?{想象中}

When I saw you running over with your fishing rod,
I think I heard the fish quickly swimming away.
Next time, try to be a bit lighter on your feet.{开心}

The result? I did catch something with a peculiar silhouette...
But it escaped under the cover of night.
To this day, I still wonder what it was...{思考}
